
# Project Title

A brief description of what this project does and who it's for

Built an app that helps user to keep track of their daily tasks. This app has multiple in built features such as stopwatch, timer, worldclock and calendar. Made use of Java Swing framework and complex algorithms to provide users with accurate results.
